{"tid":2005704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勿忘初衷，五大訴求，缺一不可","createTime":"2020-05-07T09:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T09:54:39.000Z","uid":58750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84e2a81b22ba1d0758b4e491ddf1d69857d0b326","tid":2005704,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"六．一二 下個月都就快一週年，你地仲記唔記得五大訴求係咩？<br />\n唔記得就睇下，勿忘初衷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1 全面撤回《逃犯條例》修訂草案<br />\n2 撤回「暴動」定性(包含612)<br />\n3 撤銷所有反送中示威者控罪<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4 成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警隊濫權情況</span><br />\n5 立即實行「真雙普選」</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6c88ddacaf52ca040deaf27f65946bee17418247","tid":2005704,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:35:29.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"36b97bd5a8c70b18985a42396e810e4cc8127120","tid":2005704,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"cb2810b4111aee630181df409764f0f9b4bb4486","tid":2005704,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:36:26.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"4be50af675ed71a447d06aeda4b7a82ca169dfea","tid":2005704,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"10682ff2acc463e20bd64a67818a040d5894c423","tid":2005704,"uid":209644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e53d148fe100f8cc529d705443cb9431409919f","tid":2005704,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"仲有一頂 解散警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji